title: The High Costs of Cardtronics’ ATMs
text:
Growth, like beauty, is often in the eye of the beholder.
In management’s eyes, growth is booming at Cardtronics. In late July, the largest U.S. nonbank ATM operator’s second-quarter results showed adjusted net income per diluted share of 71 cents, up 16% from a year earlier. Adjusted earnings before interest, taxes, depreciation and...
